{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c22d3b22bc","title":"中学教师的右派言论（一）","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（四）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编印，1957年11月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1375b812ef","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"c22d3b22bc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0fa7d3988d","name":"山西"},{"id":"25a6dd25b0","name":"刘桐"},{"id":"2ce791befd","name":"王衷英"},{"id":"6ebe7744d3","name":"胡友西"},{"id":"ef770720a2","name":"唐芸"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b7f1520e4d","type":"title","text":"中学教师的右派言论（一）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"c3d1d4a856","type":"authors","text":"山西胡友西王衷英刘桐唐芸","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"1c3663ad39","type":"paragraph","text":"胡友西（大同一中教师）：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"a4e9028757","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在知识分子没有发挥出潜力，是受了打击，有负担。知识分子怎样也是摇旗呐喊，真正的模范是党、团员”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"037697a74d","type":"paragraph","text":"王衷英（长治二中教师）：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"a211b4b221","type":"paragraph","text":"“党对知识分子是扩大缺点，原则有余，关怀不足；要求有余，支持不足；怀疑有余，信任不足。往往一阵风就难当。知识分子卖力不讨好，几次运动整的知识分子气节丧失净尽”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"677c6bd76f","type":"paragraph","text":"刘桐（平定二中教师）：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"170e578c43","type":"paragraph","text":"“许多地方许多人，对知识分子的面貌还缺乏正确的认识，对知识分子的团结、使用、关心没有多少变动，越下边越如此。知识分子被怀疑、闲置，甚至还有挨斗争的，恐恐然，惶惶然”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"fa743c73fc","type":"paragraph","text":"唐芸（太原机械学校教师）：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"},{"id":"3c3e26e490","type":"paragraph","text":"“你们说共产党的政策是对的，只不过下来后个别干部搞错了，你们难道真的糊涂了吗？要是不错，共产党中央没有指示，那么各地知识分子，尤其是高级知识分子都遭殃呢？别再天真啰”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc"}],"page":{"id":"cf18f79377","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c22d3b22bc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}